message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product for $95. This is a limited-time offer, so don't hesitate to accept it!
Thanks for the offer Alice, but I'm looking to spend a bit less. How about $85? I'm very interested in your product.
I appreciate your interest in our product, Bob. After careful consideration, I am willing to consider your offer at $90. Please let me know if this works for you.
